    'blog.art17.excerpt': 'After a refusal, IRCC\'s letter is often vague. An ATIP request gives you access to the officer\'s internal notes (GCMS notes) — essential for understanding the real reasons behind the decision.',
    'blog.art17.kw1':     'ATIP request',
